  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5782110">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5782110/" class="title-link">光焰永存</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5782110"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yyyfmmm/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3428097-23.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yyyfmmm/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晏砚兰心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-18"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-18 07:47:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5782110_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  胡适这个名字在我的脑海里一直像是一道光，也似一个谜。因才疏学浅，所受到的正统教育中又未曾有丝毫接触他的作品的地方，直到自己在各种渠道每每听闻他的名字，都也有些浅尝辄止欲说还休，在印象中，他一直就是个“反面人物”，与鲁迅等人是完全对立的那种人，也幸好我们的时...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5782110/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5782110_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5782110_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评17篇
                </a>
